reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars Fantastic, beautiful shelf
reviews.reviewText: I'm glad I bought it. I bought 2 because I had a lot stuff that I wanted to unpack from boxes. I enjoy looking at my stuff on the shelf. Its beautiful to me. I think the shape is nice. The top is bit wobbly, but still connects and holds together well with its twin. It was fairly easy to assemble. I needed a ladder for levels 5 & 6. It fit everything I wanted it to and more. It was everything I wanted.It would be a 5 star review but I can already tell that when I move... it won't be easy to transport unless disassembled.
